Real Steel World Robot Boxing packs bigger punches, harder-hitting battles, and double the action of its predecessor with better graphics, brand new robots, more modes and head-to-head multiplayer. In the not-so-distant future where boxing is taken to the extreme, people and robots synch up for a larger-than-life entertainment experience. Pilot a bot-crushing behemoth and jab, uppercut and haymaker your way to victory!


A total of 24 mean machines, including fan favorite superstars such as Zeus, Atom and Twin Cities. Now eight new contenders have entered the ring; brawl as Touchdown, HollowJack, Blockbuster, Biowar and more!
10 different arenas that barely contain these hulking mechanical brutes.
Championship, Time Attack, Daily Exhibition and Free Sparring; four diverse modes that will test your mettle AND your metal.
Bigger, better and now social! Take on friends in live local Wi-Fi multiplayer and fight your way up the leaderboards.
Customize with decals, load up with upgrades and get a fighting edge with power-ups!
The movie springs to life with new special moves and cinematic Rip-Offs.
